location: 200 south Garey st., Los Angeles, CA 90012.
description: Artists: Revok, Rime, Askew One, Deus, Vans, Score, Dabs & Myla, and Witness. The mural is divided into four sections with color schemes that correspond to different seasons of the year. The word 'Only' represents winter - Rime, Witness and letters by Vans. The word 'Time' represents spring - Dabs & Myla and letter by Score. The word 'Will' represents summer - Rime and letters by Revok. The word 'Tell' represents fall - Deus and letters by Askew. In 2011 this mural was covered by a wheat paste and was later uncovered.
